\int_0^\infty \frac{\sin^2(x) }{(1 + x)^2} dx
\lim_{t\rightarrow\infty}\int_0^t \frac{\sin^2(x) }{(1 + x)^2} dx
\int_0^\infty \frac{\sin^2x}{(1+x)^2}dx+\int_0^\infty \frac{\cos^2x}{(1+x)^2}dx=\int_0^\infty \frac{1}{(1+x)^2}dx
\lim_{t\rightarrow \infty} \int_0^t \frac{1}{(1+x)^2}dx=\lim_{t\rightarrow \infty}[1-\frac{1}{1+t}]=1
\sin^2x\over (1+x)^2
